targets.target: match (n:JIRA) where n.sprintId in $SprintID return DISTINCT n.sprintId
match (n:JIRA) where n.sprintId in $SprintID return count(n) as Count
match (a:JIRA)-[r:FROM_JIRA_TO_GIT]->(b:GIT) where a.sprintId in $SprintID with count(DISTINCT b.commitId) as Count  return Count

match (a:JIRA)-[r:FROM_JIRA_TO_GIT]->(b:GIT) where a.sprintId in $SprintID with count(b) as Count match (a:JIRA)-[r:FROM_JIRA_TO_GIT]->(b:GIT) where a.sprintId in $SprintID return count(b)+Count as Total

MATCH (n:JIRA)-[:FROM_JIRA_TO_GIT]->(m:GIT)  WHERE n.sprintId IN $SprintID WITH distinct m as git
MATCH (git)-[:FROM_GIT_TO_JENKINS]->(n:JENKINS) with distinct n.buildNumber as buildNumber return count(buildNumber) as Count

MATCH (n:JIRA)-[:FROM_JIRA_TO_GIT]->(m:GIT)  WHERE n.sprintId IN $SprintID WITH distinct m as git
MATCH (git)-[:FROM_GIT_TO_JENKINS]->(n:JENKINS) WITH distinct n as jenkins
MATCH (jenkins)-[:FROM_JENKINS_TO_RUNDECK]->(n:RUNDECK) with distinct n.jenkineBuildNumber as Deployments return count(Deployments )
match (a:JIRA)-[r:FROM_JIRA_TO_GIT]->(b:GIT) where a.sprintId in $SprintID return count(DISTINCT b.gitAuthorName) as Count
match (n:DEFECTS) where n.SprintID in $SprintID return count(n) as Count
match (n:DEFECTS) where n.SprintID in $SprintID return DISTINCT n.DefectDuring as Type, count(n) as Count order by Count desc
match (a:JIRA)-[r:FROM_JIRA_TO_GIT]->(b:GIT)  where a.sprintId in $SprintID return DISTINCT b.gitAuthorName as Developer, count(DISTINCT b.gitCommitId) as Count order by Count desc limit 5
match (a:DEFECTS) where a.SprintID in $SprintID return DISTINCT a.AssignedTo as Developer, count(a.DefectID) as Count order by Count desc limit 5

MATCH (n:JIRA)-[:FROM_JIRA_TO_GIT]->(m:GIT)  WHERE n.sprintId IN $SprintID WITH distinct m as git
MATCH (git)-[:FROM_GIT_TO_JENKINS]->(n:JENKINS) with distinct n.duration  as Duration return ceil(avg(toInt(Duration ))) as AvgTimeInSecs

MATCH (n:JIRA)-[:FROM_JIRA_TO_GIT]->(m:GIT)  WHERE n.sprintId IN $SprintID WITH distinct m as git
MATCH (git)-[:FROM_GIT_TO_JENKINS]->(n:JENKINS) with distinct n.duration  as Duration return ceil(max(toInt(Duration ))) as Build

MATCH (n:JIRA)-[:FROM_JIRA_TO_GIT]->(m:GIT)  WHERE n.sprintId in $SprintID WITH distinct m as git
MATCH (git)-[:FROM_GIT_TO_JENKINS]->(n:JENKINS) WHERE n.status="Failure" WITH distinct n.buildNumber as buildNumber  return buildNumber.inSightsTimeX as inSightsTimeX, count(buildNumber) as Failed order by inSightsTimeX

MATCH (n:JIRA)-[:FROM_JIRA_TO_GIT]->(m:GIT)  WHERE n.sprintId in $SprintID WITH distinct m as git
MATCH (git)-[:FROM_GIT_TO_JENKINS]->(n:JENKINS) WHERE n.status="Success" WITH distinct n.buildNumber as buildNumber  return buildNumber.inSightsTimeX as inSightsTimeX, count(status) as Success order by inSightsTimeX
match (n:RUNDECK) where n.jenkineBuildNumber in $buildNumber return ceil(avg(toInt(n.jenkineBuildNumber))) as AvgTimeInSecs
match (n:RUNDECK) where n.jenkineBuildNumber in $buildNumber return ceil(max(toInt(n.duration))) as Deploy

MATCH (n:JIRA)-[:FROM_JIRA_TO_GIT]->(m:GIT)  WHERE n.sprintId IN $SprintID WITH distinct m as git
MATCH (git)-[:FROM_GIT_TO_JENKINS]->(n:JENKINS) WITH distinct n as jenkins
MATCH (jenkins)-[:FROM_JENKINS_TO_RUNDECK]->(n:RUNDECK) where n.status='Failure' with distinct n.jenkineBuildNumber as Deployments return n.inSightsTimeX as inSightsTimeX, count(Deployments) as Failed order by inSightsTimeX

MATCH (n:JIRA)-[:FROM_JIRA_TO_GIT]->(m:GIT)  WHERE n.sprintId IN $SprintID WITH distinct m as git
MATCH (git)-[:FROM_GIT_TO_JENKINS]->(n:JENKINS) WITH distinct n as jenkins
MATCH (jenkins)-[:FROM_JENKINS_TO_RUNDECK]->(n:RUNDECK) where n.status='Success' with distinct n.jenkineBuildNumber as Deployments return n.inSightsTimeX as inSightsTimeX, count(Deployments) as Success order by inSightsTimeX
